        <briefdescription>
<para>Registers a component type with the reflection system. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Generates `ComponentOps` function pointers based on which lifecycle hooks the type implements. Uses `if constexpr` for zero-overhead when hooks are not present.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>T</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The component type to register. Must be copy-constructible for cloning support. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
